{"type":"message","id":"098b8344","parentId":"3a34639b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:38:59.488Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:d5964274-e7d4-4a4d-a6fb-59d1ce026dc0 Sandbox-Pulse-10min] Run the sandbox pulse and report the result.\n\nExecute: C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1\n\nRead the most recent pulse log from C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\ ( newest file ). Extract the OBSERVATION and any applied mutations. Reply with a concise summary of what happened in this pulse cycle.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 10:38 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-24 02:38 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774319939484}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f94472e","parentId":"098b8344","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:39:04.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run the sandbox pulse script and then read the most recent pulse log.","thinkingSignature":"b6e71501a34857712291f8744d0f587f1e7c91050d04c2a138c63e9ee03e0c6c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4t7vs15gp94a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1","timeout":120}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4t7vs15gp94a_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\ | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 1 | Get-Content","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":133,"cacheRead":4246,"cacheWrite":7824,"totalTokens":12246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774319939487}}
